<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Zaginiona Ścieżka</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel+Decorative:wght@400;700;900&family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        :root { --bg-deep: #05080a; --gold-text: linear-gradient(to bottom, #fcf6ba, #bf953f); }
        body { background-color: var(--bg-deep); color: #bf953f; font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; overflow: hidden; }
        .runic { font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', cursive; }
        .gold-text { background: var(--gold-text); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; }
        .mist {
            position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, transparent 20%, #05080a 90%);
            z-index: 1; pointer-events: none;
        }
        .rune-bg {
            position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            font-size: 20rem; opacity: 0.03; font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', cursive;
            pointer-events: none; user-select: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-screen text-center p-4">

    <div class="rune-bg">ᛟ</div>
    <div class="mist"></div>

    <main class="relative z-10 max-w-lg border-y border-[#334155] py-12 px-6 bg-[#05080a]/80 backdrop-blur-sm shadow-2xl">
        <h1 class="runic text-8xl mb-2 font-black gold-text">404</h1>
        <h2 class="text-2xl tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-slate-400 mb-6">Ścieżka Zaginęła</h2>

        <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            Wygląda na to, że zabłądziłeś we mgle. <br>
            Ten token zaproszenia nie istnieje w naszych księgach lub został wpisany błędnie.
        </p>

        <div class="w-16 h-[1px] bg-[#bf953f] mx-auto mb-8 opacity-50"></div>

        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 italic">
            Sprawdź link w wiadomości, którą otrzymałeś.
        </p>
    </main>

</body>
</html>